Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: default-jre | java11-runtime
Maintainer: CircuitSim Maintainers <noreply@example.com>
Description: Digital Circuit Simulator
 A Java Swing-based digital combinational logic simulator.
 It supports interactive wiring, live simulation, XML save/load,
 and truth-table generation.
